Theorem: tree_induction

   ⊢ ∀P0 P1.
       (∀l. P1 l ⇒ ∀a. P0 (Node a l)) ∧ P1 [] ∧
       (∀t l. P0 t ∧ P1 l ⇒ P1 (t::l)) ⇒
       (∀t. P0 t) ∧ ∀l. P1 l

Auxiliary definitions:

   ⊢ ∀P0 l a. Lam_47 P0 l a ⇔ P0 (Node a l)
   ⊢ ∀P1 P0 l. Lam_48 P1 P0 l ⇔ P1 l ⇒ $! (Lam_47 P0 l)
   ⊢ ∀P0 t P1 l. Lam_49 P0 t P1 l ⇔ P0 t ∧ P1 l ⇒ P1 (t::l)
   ⊢ ∀P0 P1 t. Lam_50 P0 P1 t ⇔ $! (Lam_49 P0 t P1)
   ⊢ ∀P0 t. Lam_51 P0 t ⇔ P0 t
   ⊢ ∀P1 l. Lam_52 P1 l ⇔ P1 l

Lifted theorem:

   ⊢ ∀P0 P1.
       $! (Lam_48 P1 P0) ∧ P1 [] ∧ $! (Lam_50 P0 P1) ⇒
       $! (Lam_51 P0) ∧ $! (Lam_52 P1)
|#

